ass=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">配偶栏写的丈夫哥哥名字<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">【女子结婚15年后欲离婚，才发现结婚证配偶栏写的丈夫哥哥名字，民政局：无法撤销】安徽亳州，周女士想和丈夫离婚，但结婚证上配偶一栏写的是丈夫哥哥的名字。民政局表示，无法撤销周女士的结婚登记信息，她向民政局与丈夫提起起诉，希望通过法院起诉离婚，但法院没有支持。周女士不服，已再次上诉。 ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/b99a0d3fd09681a7_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot04\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/b99a0d3fd09681a7_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ww4.sinaimg.cn\/thumb180\/00612mXUgy1fxxfzy0haej30e81kwtbz.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/b99a0d3fd09681a7_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#李渔回头看看黄澄澄吧#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">#人不彪悍枉少年#  噫呜呜呜呜呜呜呜呜呜呜呜暴风哭泣[泪][泪][泪]好气啊啊啊啊啊啊！！李渔要不你回头看看黄澄澄吧 ！心疼黄澄澄！[泪]\n（虽然真的很希望李渔能跟杨夕这对青梅竹马能在一起，但是在杨夕眼里李渔只是个从小一起长大的好哥们而已，不管李渔对她多好，杨夕都觉得理所应当。心疼李师傅[泪] ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/2f8c7d2c2ae08220_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot05\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/2f8c7d2c2ae08220_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ww4.sinaimg.cn\/thumb180\/005GEatSgy1fxw1cgqhb0j30v94mok9l.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/2f8c7d2c2ae08220_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#naomi#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">#naomi豆瓣# 作为一个知道naomi分手内部详情的人，#naomi chace#真的看不下去naomikyx恶心的举动了 #naomi 瓜# ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n    <div class=\"UG_box_foot\">\n        <a href=\"\/\/weibo.com\/a\/hot\/realtime\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">查看更多<i class=\"W_ficon ficon_arrow_right S_ficon\">a<\/i><\/a>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n"})</script>
